reviews.review_text: I Was One of the Few In Attendance This is an excellent recording of an excellent show. My roommate and I were freshmen at UW and -- freezing weather and windchill be darned -- got to the coliseum well before the show to get good seats. Turned out to be unnecessary, because (i) the doors were closed, and (ii) it was so cold that the place was 3/4 empty (and I might be overstating the size of the "crowd").  All in all, an unforgettable experience... Thank you for the recording!
